YOU MAY EVEN FIND SOMETHING YOU LOST The South African Police Service in Grahamstown will be holding a public auction on Thursday 26 January 2017 at 10am at the police station at 16 Beaufort Street. Viewing from 8am at the same premises. Items on auction include building materials, electronic equipment and bicycles. For more information about the auction, contact Warrant Officer Zwide at 046 603 9111.